{
  "stem": "14429.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "For the life of me, I could not see how he could have done it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I felt I was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in a place where there was no escape, no escape.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Even if I would have had a crowbar, I would not have been able to do-- and good for him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He would never have survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He was too weak and sick, but we-- he had so much guts.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Wait till you hear my, my, my brother Leon's stories.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He had a lot of guts, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "In other words, when it depends on your life, you become resourceful.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "You find extra energy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But only the realization came to me when I was in the cattle car what actually happened.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Therefore, I want to bring something out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Nobody that wasn't there can really understand the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The only-- we only talk about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "You can understand-- you can-- everybody can understand what they're saying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But it is really incomprehensible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "The only thing that shows the truth are the pictures that were taken by the liberation, by the-- by the-- by the liberation armies that took the pictures directly in the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Those were the true pictures.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Everything else is just imitation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "This is-- are the true pictures.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Because only when I was in the cattle car did I understand what my brother did.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were like cattles in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "It is really made for cattles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "We had one big problem in there, in that car.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "There was a pregnant woman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "She was gaunt.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "She must have been in her sixth month easily.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "But she was losing her mind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "She started to fantasize-- and losing her mind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And my-- Blanca tended to her.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
